Packegs nodes:
 - scanner_3d

scanner_3d node:
Listens on /lidar3d topic and transmitts position data to serial device controlling laser.

Run:
$ roslaunch ri_sensor_scanner_3d scanner_3d

View 3D scan with rviz:
1. Set base frame to /base_link
2. Subscribe /scan with laser plugin
NOTE: make sure laser frame_id is set to /laser_link by your laser driver
